reviews.text: The food was interesting as we had a salad buffet then paid for our set meals. The food was good and atmosphere was done up for weddings.  If you want to do a wedding banquet there then it’s a fairly nice venue. They also do test menus for weddings for the soon to be newlyweds

The wedding hall is too small & narrow. 
Foods are really bad taste. Vegetable is too salty. The  fried rice is flat taste. Wonton is cold & wonton skin is hard & sticky that should be leave it for long time. Highly not  recommended.
Nice buffet banquet witg movenpick icecream XD  good venue for small banquet for about 10 tables

Food, service and environment is excellent at reasonable higher price.  Since the place was a wedding hall, only few visitors had lunch here and very suitable for private conversation.  There was an outdoor balcony or platform for marriage ceremony which created a romantic atmosphere.  Reach the restaurant from lift plus elevator would be faster.
